These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, canasta, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Game        | snooker | chess   | monopoly | canasta    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: liverpool, berlin, boston, new-york
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | new-york    | liverpool | boston | berlin    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, snowboarding, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | water-polo | snowboarding | biathlon    | baseball      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person drinking water is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | lemonade | tea | water | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, gardening, chess, skydiving
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | chess | gardening |

