.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, fonseca, prince, davidoff
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, japanese, malaysian
1. the italian is in an even position##4
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the italian##1
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar   | prince      | fonseca | davidoff | siglo |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian     | indonesian  | japanese  |

