.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, go, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Game     | backgammon | go  | whist     | monopoly |

