.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, dannemann, blend, bongani
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
2. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the dunhill-smoker and the owner of the goat##2
8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Cigar   | dannemann | dunhill      | bongani | blend |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

