.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
City: san-francisco, berlin, nizza, boston
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person traveling to nizza##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to nizza is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | boston | berlin   | san-francisco | nizza |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

