.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, bird, goldfish
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the hamster and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Pet   | bird | ferret | goldfish        | hamster    |

