.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, musical, adventure, satire
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, satire-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is satire-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is satire-polo is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | satire   | musical      | adventure      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | satire-polo | biathlon |

