.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, d&b, dubstep, rock
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, snake
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | rock | techno | d&b |
| Pet           | snake     | dog     | goat   | frog         |

