.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, funk, soul, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
5. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | trance | soul    | r&b |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

