.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsiris is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
5. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | iris  | amaryllis     | daffodil |

