.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, rat, pony
There 4 different types of food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
7. the person eating corn is the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Pet   | pony | lizard    | rat       | snake |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

