.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, spinach, strawberry, cauliflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, tram, trike
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food   | spinach | strawberry | cherry  | cauliflower |
| Transport     | bus      | tram       | motorbike | trike     |

