.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, fish, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the owner of the mouse and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse | fish   | guinea-pig | cat |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 